{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That town didn't get a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were just all shipped straight out to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By the way, I didn't mention to you that the majority of the town-- the majority of the Jews in town when we were on the capital market, were then taken to the station and shipped off to Belzec to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so when my Uncle Abraham with his children and-- and practically about 80% of all Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this is what-- when I talk to some of the churches or schools and I tell them, you know, that most people think that the Jews died in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They died long before that. 80% of our town was gone that July, August.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They all went straight there and were killed the same day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, they came December 4, and they said now the ghetto is going to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So-- the day before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So now we knew this is it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So my father decided that we better go and hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I, my father-- not my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was shipped to Jaslo to clean up from that-- from the liquidation of the Jews there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So he was there together with about 15 other Jews from our town to clean up there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so my father, I, my little brother, my-- my cousin Moshe, and his wife, the one who escaped from the transport, and their two little blonde children, [INAUDIBLE] about three years old-- two, three years old, we went out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And in the store where we had, there was a basement where you lifted off the cover.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there was a ladder you went into the basement.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
